  "texts": [
    "Similar measurements were conducted for PE, PTFE, PMMA, and Nylon (Suppl. Figs.",
    "19-21 and Suppl.",
    "Each polymer generates a characteristic array of peaks on the AgF@AgM@C10 substrate.",
    "Nonetheless, the same trend in EF was observed, with AgF@AgM@C10 showing the highest EF followed by AgM@C10, Klarite, and glass.",
    "Researchers typically collect MPs in the environment by trawling through polluted water using Neuston nets or equivalent."
